{"tid":2245772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[擠錄音牙膏]立榮航空飛東沙被迫返航 民航局公布錄音檔抄件還原始末","createTime":"2020-10-16T13:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T08:03:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":260,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c62c8e24fd378547dda061d280d145acd4c4f1","tid":2245772,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3323738\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3323738&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVUyHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=4b3660aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Flife%2Fbreakingnews%2F3323738&h=f79ab815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/life/breakingnews/3323738</a><br />\n<br />\n〔記者鄭瑋奇／台北報導〕昨日上午我國立榮航空由高雄小港機場飛往東沙的軍包機，機上載有海巡署等工作人員約55人，被香港區管中心拒絕進入飛航情報區，立榮航班立即掉頭回台灣；不過今日傳出香港民航處說明，是台灣航空管制中心自行取消航班進入香港飛行情報區的要求。對此，交通部民用航空局今晚公布通聯紀錄，還原立榮東沙包機被迫返航事件過程。<br />\n<br />\n根據錄音抄件內容顯示，在雙方航管交接立榮9051航班過程中，香港區管中心在昨天上午9點36分突然致電我方區管中心，表示「&hellip;&hellip; we have got a danger area west of kapli actually its very close to kapli over looking traffic and the safty altitude is flight level two six zero or above（我們有一個危險區在kapli航點西面非常接近kapli相關航空器安全高度要在26000呎或以上）」<br />\n<br />\n民航局表示，由於港方事先並未發布飛航公告，也未告知我方此一訊息，我方航管人員向對方表達並不知道此事，由於立榮航機最高飛行高度為2萬5000呎，反覆確認後，港方表示「hong kong cannot accept this aircraft（香港無法接受該航空器）。」後續我方航管人員再次確認對方態度後，只好通知立榮9051航班機師，機師基於安全考量，決定返航，我方隨後通報港方此一情況。<br />\n<br />\n雙方對話記錄顯示，班機返航關鍵在於港方突然表示有「危險區域」，甚至直言「無法接受該航空器」，機師基於飛安只好返航，我方是被迫返航，並非港方所稱主動取消。民航局呼籲港方，應釐清並說明這次事件過程及原因，並希望類似影響飛安事件不再發生，也期待港方未來應依照國際規範，和我方共同維護國際飛航的安全及秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/10/16/phprKZDeu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F10%2F16%2FphprKZDeu.jpg&h=299f9745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">on9港共你估而家無錄音呀</span>"},{"pid":"36a0e2d7acbe908b811e3a4dc8848f3562eb2f8d","tid":2245772,"uid":155818,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:07:35.000Z","msg":"學埋支那做埋哂D陰質小動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44b5f6b18e7cac33ee5d97e75714065323020f1","tid":2245772,"uid":4783,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"香港民航局話無講過架<br />\n台灣一定係呃人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學人講大話真係on9"},{"pid":"a811518c1cf232d9e3f91cd11bae39d41e345585","tid":2245772,"uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"b44b5f6b18e7cac33ee5d97e75714065323020f1","tid":2245772,"uid":4783,"like":58,"dislike":1,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"香港民航局話無講過架<br />\n台灣一定係呃人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學人講大話真係on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:09:55.000Z","msg":"再唔認就放埋段clip上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff99e57c22a15b7146b3af1b73eed6b6c390dec","tid":2245772,"uid":68598,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:12:07.000Z","msg":"7撚到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b45a25f57109c7f7992a77403a669543d9fdc837","tid":2245772,"uid":302471,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T13:12:56.000Z",